or conta própria. Descobrindo uma rede de crime, fraude e corrupçăo que se propaga por dois condados, Alden se vę preso entre os planos de uma organizaçăo criminosa sem seu distintivo e sem ajuda, com uma única aliada, Maddie (Patricia Richardson, Home Improvement, Nos Bastidores do Poder). Querendo justiça a qualquer preço, Alden decide descobrir quem está por trás da organizaçăo criminosa, mesmo que seja preciso ultrapassar os limites." type="movie" contentRating="A14" duration="7200000" originallyAvailableAt="2025-03-31T00:00:00Z" requiresConsent="1" skipParent="1" thumb="https://img.static-ottera.com/prod/ime/video/thumbnails/poster/2000x2858/clin_bpo_poster.jpg" title="County Line" userState="0" year="2025"><Image alt="County Line" type="coverArt" url="https://img.static-ottera.com/prod/ime/video/thumbnails/widescreen/3840x2160/clin_bpo_horizontal.jpg"/><Image alt="County Line" type="coverPoster" url="https://img.static-ottera.com/prod/ime/video/thumbnails/poster/2000x2858/clin_bpo_poster.jpg"/><Genre filter="genre=6a0c2728768cf9b31f6fe02a" id="6a0c2728768cf9b31f6fe02a" key="/library/sections/home/all?genre=6a0c2728768cf9b31f6fe02a" ratingKey="genre_6a0c2728768cf9b31f6fe02a" slug="bingeworthy" tag="Bingeworthy" type="directory" context="tag.genre"/><Genre filter="genre=6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" id="6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" key="/library/sections/home/all?genre=6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" ratingKey="genre_6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" slug="drama" tag="Drama" type="directory" context="tag.genre"/><Media beginsAt="1779580800" duration="7200000" endsAt="1779588000" id="6a10f71ea95e566ad16ac6f2" onAir="0" premiere="0" videoResolution="720" origin="livetv"/><Media beginsAt="1779624000" duration="7200000" endsAt="1779631200" id="6a10f71ea95e566ad16ac6fc" onAir="0" premiere="0" videoResolution="720" origin="livetv"/></Video><Video art="https://img.static-ottera.com/prod/ime/video/thumbnails/widescreen/3840x2160/clai_bpo_horizontal.jpg" guid="plex://movie/6a10f711a95e566ad1